videos.description: D'Angelo Russell throws a slick bounce pass between defenders to a cutting Naz Reid, who goes up to hammer down a powerful slam for the Timberwolves.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Russell slips a pass to Reid for thunderous jam) 2021/04/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Russell slips a pass to Reid for thunderous jam

videos.description: Jim Jackson chokes on a popcorn kernel in surprise as Karl-Anthony Towns gets the sweet pass from Ricky Rubio and goes up to throttle down a powerful and-1 dunk in the face of Ivica Zubac.
